<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='330821' id='t-330821'>In January of this year,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='333024' id='t-333024'>I went to Myanmar to interview political prisoners,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='337353' id='t-337353'>and I was surprised to find them less bitter</span>
