<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526199' id='t-526199'>We don't seek the painful experiences</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529424' id='t-529424'>that hew our identities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532100' id='t-532100'>but we seek our identities</span>
