<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537343' id='t-537343'>We cannot bear a pointless torment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='540229' id='t-540229'>but we can endure great pain</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='542729' id='t-542729'>if we believe that it's purposeful.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='545904' id='t-545904'>Ease makes less of an impression on us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548160' id='t-548160'>than struggle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='549643' id='t-549643'>We could have been ourselves without our delights,</span>
