<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='693105' id='t-693105'>Russia awakened me to the lemonade notion</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696260' id='t-696260'>that oppression breeds the power to oppose it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698814' id='t-698814'>and I gradually understood that as the cornerstone</span>
